<h1>Typeahead</h1>

<p><code>f-typeahead</code> creates a <a href="/api/havok/form/Typeahead.html">havok/form/Typeahead</a> which provides a filtering select style input.</p>

<p>Note: a typeahead must define a store to query against.</p>

